      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(agents): retry thinking-only errored turns",
        "body": "Summary\n- Fixes #91953.\n- Retries replay-safe `stopReason=\"error\"` turns when the assistant emitted only non-visible thinking content before the provider error.\n- Keeps the existing safety boundary: no retry after potential side effects, no retry when visible assistant text exists, and no retry for empty error turns with non-zero output but no thinking-only content.\n\nVerification\n- `pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run.empty-error-retry.test.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run.incomplete-turn.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `pnpm tsgo:test:src` still fails on unrelated current-main `src/agents/sessions/sdk*` `thinkingFormat: \"ollama\"` type errors; the touched files are clean after fixing the local fixture type issue.\n\nReal behavior proof\n- behavior: A replay-safe assistant turn that ends with `stopReason=\"error\"` after emitting only thinking content is retried by the embedded runner instead of surfacing a silent incomplete-turn error.\n- environment: Local source checkout at `9a6c71a47d` plus this branch, Node 22.22.2, pnpm 11.2.2, Vitest agents project.\n- steps: Added a regression that returns an Anthropic-style assistant message with `stopReason=\"error\"`, a signed thinking block, and `usage.output=1120`, followed by a successful second attempt.\n- evidence: Before the fix, the focused regression failed because `runEmbeddedAttempt` was called once instead of twice. After the fix, the full touched test files pass: 2 files, 129 tests.\n- observedResult: The runner now retries the non-visible errored thinking-only turn and completes from the successful second attempt, while side-effect and visible-progress guards remain covered.\n- notTested: I did not replay the original live Vertex AI / Claude Opus provider failure. The proof uses the embedded-runner harness to reproduce the exact terminal assistant shape from the issue and verify the shared retry path.\n",
        "branch": "ai-hpc/91953-empty-error-thinking-retry",
